## âœ¨ Features  
- ğŸ” **AI vs Human Detection** â€“ Classifies input text as *human-written* or *AI-generated*.  
- ğŸ§  **Machine Learning Models** â€“ Uses GPT-2 (Hugging Face) for classification.  
